ight-unset\" id=\"SE-661b99e4-c8ed-4d4a-8df7-1c77945e296b\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-02f06d9d-c98c-45ec-aae7-7e35ade7986a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ac49a7ca-23b1-479b-ab71-add2e1b4d378\" style=\"color:#555555;\">통상의 경우 금액만 보고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4c0256e3-1788-4651-93eb-5fbc31d15331\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-04647786-eed5-4086-8ecc-7a78fc70eeb5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">개발을 포기하는 회사가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7ae01691-ab2e-44d2-9343-71141a22088f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-28903257-c3fd-4d21-ab0a-4952d6af1a32\" style=\"color:#555555;\">왜 이 금액이 나올 수밖에 없는지는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d479d4e3-0a17-4f8b-b2d8-f6f16c3f4e89\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-62b0285c-43dd-4041-899a-245831e585b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시연 과정을 통해 설명을 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f05ac72d-360f-4b1e-bb24-19fdfa139136\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2e6eb7f5-527d-469c-8b94-446adc74981b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">반드시 직접 찾아뵙고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0707d68d-b3e6-49be-90ab-6b15a6b9b3ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\